<!-- banner -->
<div class="homepage-banner home-banner-bg">
  <div class="pr">
    <%= image_tag "home/simple-logo", alt: "alttext", class: "homepage-banner-logo" %>
    <h3 class="text-very-large text-bold">关注呼吸,<br>关爱生命</h3>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- content -->
<div class="">
  <div class="">
    <div class="color-block bg-trans-white-green ta-left pad-tb-rem4">
      <%= image_tag "home/lungs", alt: "alttext", class: "color-block-bg-image" %>
      <div class="color-block-text">
        <p class="text-large">长风药业是一家致力于为全球市场提供高品质吸入类药物的综合性专业制药公司。</p><p>在拥有丰富行业经验的高素质团队的管理下，公司专注于在最先进的设备中开发治疗呼吸系统疾病的药物。</p>
      </div>
      <!-- <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/tichel/image/upload/v1598850977/CF%20Website/Home%20page/Home_page_no_copyright4_i8sc01.jpg" alt="">
      </div> -->
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-image-area">
        <%= image_tag "home/inhalation-product-technology", alt: "alttext", class: "card-image" %>
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text">
          <p>长风药业专注于呼吸系统治疗领域产品的开发，包括：</p>
          <ul class="bulleted-list">
            <li><%= link_to "哮喘", "#{zh_therapeutic_areas_path}#Asthma" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "COPD", "#{zh_therapeutic_areas_path}#COPD" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "鼻炎", "#{zh_therapeutic_areas_path}#Rhinitis" %></li>
            <li><%= link_to "其他呼吸系统疾病", "#{zh_therapeutic_areas_path}#Other-Respiratory-Diseases" %></li>
          </ul>
          <div class="btn-area">
              <%= link_to "更多", zh_research_and_development_platform_path, class: "btn btn-flat" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card bg-blue">
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text-narrow">
          <p>根据全球市场需求，长风有20多个吸入仿制药正在开发中，还有多个护理产品可供消费者选择。</p>
          <div class="btn-area">
            <%= link_to "更多", zh_products_path, class: "btn btn-flat" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <%= image_tag "home/generics", alt: "alttext", class: "card-img-narrow" %>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="content-card">
      <div class="card-img-area">
        <img class="card-img-narrow" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/tichel/image/upload/v1598850973/CF%20Website/Home%20page/Home_page_no_copyright2_g165lc.jpg" alt="">
      </div>
      <div class="card-text-area">
        <div class="card-text-narrow">
          <p>长风药业已与多家公司建立了合作伙伴关系，将共同努力为全球市场开发新化合物创新技术和新型吸入制剂产品。此外，我们还为合作伙伴提供开发解决方案和服务，以支持您的技术和产品开发。</p>
          <div class="btn-area">
            <%= link_to "更多", zh_partnership_path, class: "btn btn-flat" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="small-container bg-grey-green margin-top">
      <div class="small-card-container">
        <h2>了解更多</h2>
      </div>
     <div class="small-card-container">
      <%= link_to zh_careers_path do %>
        <div class="small-card">
          <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/tichel/image/upload/v1598850971/CF%20Website/Home%20page/Home_page_CF_building_drfmbh.jpg" alt="">
          <div class="small-card-text white-text">
            <h4>职业发展</h4>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
      <div class="small-card">
        <img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/tichel/image/upload/v1597397247/gary-scott-nkCA4va-6k0-unsplash_szlu4i.jpg" alt="">
        <div class="small-card-text white-text">
          <h4>新闻</h4>
        </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
